  geom_line(aes(y = return_strategy_cumulative), colour = "blue", size = 1) + 
  geom_hline(yintercept = 1, colour = "black") + 
  labs(title = "Strategy Return vs Buy Hold Return", x = "Date", y = "Cumulative Return")
